By The Associated Press	   Monday's forecast calls for showers in the east, high
in the mid
70s. The west will see partly sunny skies and a high near 80.
Monday night is expected to stay cloudy with a chance of showers in
the east, low in the mid 60s. The west stays clear with some patchy
fog and a low around 55.
<TEXT>
