   Tuesday's forecast is for partly sunny skies in the east and a
high near 80. The west will be hot and humid with increasing clouds
in the afternoon and a chance of late day thunderstorms. High in
the mid 80s. Tuesday night will be cloudy with a chance of showers
and thunderstorms statewide. Low in the low 60s.
